title: Mano Antje
---
body:

The calm repose of this architect’s house reflects an unmistakable mix of Scandinavian and Japanese aesthetic. Slightly elevated with views over a valley, it’s designed with a minimal footprint to respect the unspoilt beauty of its indigenous shrub and mountain surrounds. 
